Package SocialMedia_Gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbonnementInfo
    Shows the Abonnements of the logged-in Nutzer Provides the data for the AbonnementPanel
    BeitragPanel
    Displays a Beitrag with its attributes Also shows buttons for editing/deleting/commenting/liking and the Kommentare
    DialogAnmelden
    Log-in dialog where user inserts username and password
    DialogBeitrag
    Dialog for creating a new Beitrag or Kommentar or editing an existing Beitrag or Kommentar
    DialogNutzer
    Dialog where user can change username, name, surname and password or deactivate his account
    DialogRegistrieren
    Dialog where user can register himself
    DialogServerData
    Dialog where user inserts serverAdress, serverPort and clientPort
    DialogSuchen
    Dialog where user can search for other users
    Hauptfenster
    Creates the main frame of the client
    HauptfensterReport
    Report Generator class for the graphical user interface.
    KommentarPanel
    Displays a Kommentar with buttons for editing/deleting
    Newsfeed
    Creates the content of the panelLinks and shows the Newsfeed (all Beitraege, Kommentare and Likes) of all Abonnements of the logged-in Nutzer
    NewsfeedPanel
    Creates the Newsfeed (all Beitraege, Kommentare and Likes) of all Abonnements of the logged-in Nutzer
    NutzerInfo
    Shows the username, name and surname of the logged-in Nutzer
    PinnwandPanel
    Creates the Pinnwand (all Beitraege, Kommentare and Likes) of a Nutzer
